# Atlas Grid — UI guidelines (frontend)

Before changing layout, forms, or styles in `decision-matrix/frontend`, read the full guide:

**[docs/architecture/ui-guidelines.md](../../docs/architecture/ui-guidelines.md)**

## Quick rules

1. **Colors** — use CSS variables (`var(--primary)`, `var(--surface)`, `var(--text-muted)`). No raw hex in new UI code except map subtype colors (`mapIcons.ts`).

2. **Primitives** — reuse existing building blocks:
   - Buttons: `.btn`, `.btn-primary`, `.btn-secondary`, `.btn-ghost`, `.btn-sm`
   - Forms: `.form-group`, `.input`; selects: `AppSelect`
   - Modals: `AppModal` + `.app-modal-*` (styles in `src/styles/components/app-modal/core.css`)
   - Page shell: `.page-header`, `.page-title`, `.subtitle`, `.card`

3. **Object detail / dense forms** — use wrappers from `components/objectDetailPanel/panelUi.tsx`:
   `PanelSection`, `FieldLabel`, `PanelSwitch`, `DetailPanelTabs`, pair-grid classes (`object-detail-panel__pair-grid*`).

4. **CSS naming** — feature prefix + BEM (`import-3d-*`, `object-detail-panel__*`). New feature styles → `src/styles/features/<feature>.css`; map styles → `src/styles/features/map/` (see `styles/README.md`). Manifest: `scripts/css-segments.mjs`; run `npm run verify:css` after global CSS changes.

5. **Tailwind** — layout utilities only (`flex`, `gap`, `shrink-0`). Do not recreate buttons/inputs with Tailwind.

6. **Icons** — Lucide; ~15–20px in panels/tabs.

7. **Dark theme** — tokens switch via `[data-theme="dark"]`; smoke-check both themes.

8. **Do not** rename existing CSS classes or break `pair-grid` without checking all object-detail tabs.

9. **Map / React Flow** — keep `map-*` and flow canvas styles separate; see map-3d-features.md for 3D.
